WEBVTT

00:01.160 --> 00:02.911
<i>Previously on</i>
The Big Bang Theory:

00:03.030 --> 00:04.979
This is just a minor setback.

00:05.030 --> 00:06.146
No, it's not, okay?

00:06.148 --> 00:07.714
I've been out here
for, like, ten years.

00:07.716 --> 00:09.283
I have nothing to show for it.

00:09.285 --> 00:11.201
Well, you have me.

00:12.036 --> 00:14.404
I do have you.

00:14.406 --> 00:15.656
(laughs)
(laughs)

00:15.658 --> 00:17.875
(sighs)

00:19.527 --> 00:22.112
Leonard Hofstadter,

00:22.114 --> 00:24.715
will you marry me?

00:29.003 --> 00:32.389
Did you seriously
just say, "Um..."?

00:33.675 --> 00:35.342
It's an outrage.
I know.

00:35.344 --> 00:37.895
The university-- they think
they can do whatever they want.

00:37.897 --> 00:40.147
We just have to sit
there and take it.

00:40.149 --> 00:41.849
You need to let it go, Sheldon.

00:41.851 --> 00:44.601
You work tirelessly for someone,
and this is what you get.

00:44.603 --> 00:45.853
Oh, my God!

00:45.855 --> 00:48.355
They're just making you
use your vacation days!

00:48.357 --> 00:50.357
But I don't want
a vacation.

00:50.359 --> 00:53.093
Okay, listen,
I don't mean to diminish

00:53.095 --> 00:54.828
what you're going through,

00:54.830 --> 00:56.530
but I'm a little
distracted right now.

00:56.532 --> 00:58.315
Oh, this again? So,

00:58.317 --> 00:59.833
Penny proposed,
you didn't say yes,

00:59.835 --> 01:02.452
and now you think you may have
lost her love forever.

01:02.454 --> 01:04.486
How does this compare
to me being forced

01:04.489 --> 01:06.540
to relax for a few days?

01:08.459 --> 01:10.677
It doesn't!
Thank you!

01:12.764 --> 01:14.348
I'm gonna go
talk to Penny.

01:14.350 --> 01:17.217
I'm going to go inside,
put on my coziest pajamas,

01:17.219 --> 01:18.752
curl up with a good book

01:18.754 --> 01:21.805
and wait for this nightmare
to be over.

01:21.807 --> 01:23.974
(sighs)

01:25.310 --> 01:28.111
Penny.

01:32.033 --> 01:34.234
Sorry.

01:35.119 --> 01:37.512
Hi.
Hey.

01:37.513 --> 01:39.563
Look, I'm sorry
I didn't text you back.

01:39.041 --> 01:40.490
I just needed
some time to think.

01:40.492 --> 01:42.543
Okay.
Here. Come in.

01:42.545 --> 01:44.411
Look, if you want
to break up, just say it.

01:44.413 --> 01:46.213
Leonard...
No, no, no, no. I take it back.

01:46.215 --> 01:48.582
Don't say it. Just-just hate me,
but stay with me.

01:48.584 --> 01:50.133
It worked for my parents.

01:51.803 --> 01:54.788
Listen, I don't want
to break up with you.

01:54.790 --> 01:56.840
Oh. O-Okay.

01:56.842 --> 01:58.342
Good, good.

01:58.344 --> 01:59.359
(laughs)

01:59.361 --> 02:01.595
So, it's cool if I cry a little?

02:02.480 --> 02:04.481
Yeah, I probably wouldn't.

02:04.483 --> 02:07.034
Yeah.

02:07.036 --> 02:08.134
(clearing throat)

02:08.137 --> 02:10.270
Look, you did the
right thing last night.

02:10.271 --> 02:11.672
I was a mess.

02:11.674 --> 02:14.424
I was just frustrated because
my career is going nowhere.

02:14.426 --> 02:16.559
Look, I get it,
and I want you to know

02:16.561 --> 02:18.695
that I support whatever
you want to do.

02:18.697 --> 02:19.997
Great, because
I've been thinking,

02:19.999 --> 02:21.949
if I really want this
acting thing to work,

02:21.951 --> 02:23.850
I need to focus all
my energy on it.

02:23.852 --> 02:25.152
And to do that,

02:25.154 --> 02:26.620
I should quit waitressing

02:26.622 --> 02:28.238
at The Cheesecake Factory.

02:28.240 --> 02:29.957
Wow!

02:29.959 --> 02:31.625
That-That's a big step.

02:31.627 --> 02:33.327
I know.
So, you know,

02:33.329 --> 02:34.511
before making any rash...

02:34.513 --> 02:36.697
I already quit.
And I support you!

02:38.299 --> 02:41.935
♪ Our whole universe
was in a hot, dense state ♪

02:41.937 --> 02:45.272
♪ Then nearly 14 billion years
ago expansion started... Wait! ♪

02:45.274 --> 02:46.857
♪ The Earth began to cool

02:46.859 --> 02:49.443
♪ The autotrophs began to drool,
Neanderthals developed tools ♪

02:49.445 --> 02:52.079
♪ We built the Wall
♪ <i>We built the pyramids</i> ♪

02:52.081 --> 02:54.748
♪ Math, Science, History,
unraveling the mystery ♪

02:54.750 --> 02:56.599
♪ That all started
with a big bang ♪

02:56.601 --> 02:58.652
♪ <i>Bang!</i> ♪

02:58.659 --> 03:02.659
<font color=#00FF00>♪ The Big Bang Theory 7x13 ♪</font>
